<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.2.5">
<l>pāla ṉāki ñālamēḻu muṇṭupaṇ ṭālilaimēl</l>
<l>cāla nāḷum paḷḷikoḷḷun tāmaraik kaṇṇaṉeṇṇil</l>
<l>nīla mārvaṇ ṭuṇṭuvāḻum neytalan taṇkaḻaṉi</l>
<l>yēla nāṟum paimpuṟavi levvuḷ kiṭantāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lotus-eyed [lord] who took to [his] bed for many days once</l>
<l>As a babe on a banyan leaf, having eaten the seven worlds,</l>
<l>He is the one who lies in Evvuḷ in green groves, where cardamom wafts,</l>
<l>With lovely, fresh paddy fields with lilies where flourish</l>
<l rend="indent">countless sapphire-like bees sipping [nectar].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
